{"sn10.4:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 10.4 ","sn10.4:0.2":"1. Indakavagga ","sn10.4:0.3":"Manibhaddasutta ","sn10.4:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava magadhesu viharati manimalike cetiye manibhaddassa yakkhassa bhavane. ","sn10.4:1.2":"Atha kho manibhaddo yakkho yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn10.4:2.1":"“Satimato sada bhaddam, ","sn10.4:2.2":"satima sukhamedhati; ","sn10.4:2.3":"Satimato suve seyyo, ","sn10.4:2.4":"vera ca parimuccati”ti. ","sn10.4:3.1":"“Satimato sada bhaddam, ","sn10.4:3.2":"satima sukhamedhati; ","sn10.4:3.3":"Satimato suve seyyo, ","sn10.4:3.4":"vera na parimuccati. ","sn10.4:4.1":"Yassa sabbamahorattam, ","sn10.4:4.2":"ahimsaya rato mano; ","sn10.4:4.3":"Mettamso sabbabhutesu, ","sn10.4:4.4":"veram tassa na kenaci”ti. "}